Defendant enters a guilty plea to Count #1 on amended information.  Court performs plea colloquy and finds Defendant guilty of Count #1 on amended information.  State gives sentencing recommendation.  Attorney Smith makes statements regarding sentencing. Attorney Smith states that Defendant will be entering DTC in Milwaukee County.  Defendant makes statements.  Court sentences the Defendant to the following:

COUNT #1:  FINE:  $515.00 & $200.00 DNA surcharge (to be paid at $50.00 per month, commencing 2/2/15, alternate 14 days jail if not paid (1 day credit given) NOTE: Defendant may pay off by performing community service at the rate of $10.00 per hour.    

  Expunction is conditionally granted after 12 months upon payment of all costs/fees and no new criminal law violations.  Defendant must Petition the Court in writing upon successful completion of the sentence.
